<sect1 id="Edit-Menu">
	<title>The Edit Menu</title>




	<para>The <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu is </para>
		<figure id="menu-edit-labelled.png">
		    <title>The <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu.</title>
		    <screenshot>
		      <graphic fileref="figures/menu-edit-labelled.png"></graphic>
		    </screenshot>
	    </figure>
	<para>The menu choices are grouped into the following groups:</para>



 <variablelist>

      <varlistentry>
	<term>
	  <guiicon><inlinegraphic fileref="figures/label-one.png"></inlinegraphic>
	    Change History.
	  </guiicon>
	</term>
	<listitem>
	  <para>These menu items allow the user to undo recent changes to a
worksheet. </para>
	</listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
	<term>
	  <guiicon><inlinegraphic fileref="figures/label-two.png"></inlinegraphic>
	    Operations on selected areas.
	  </guiicon>
	</term>
	<listitem>
	  <para>These menu items enable selected cell contents to be moved around
	a spreadsheet, moved between sheets or beween workbooks. </para>
	</listitem>
      </varlistentry>


      <varlistentry>
	<term>
	  <guiicon><inlinegraphic fileref="figures/label-three.png"></inlinegraphic>
	    Data removal operations.
	  </guiicon>
	</term>
	<listitem>
	  <para>All of these operations remove data from the worksheet. They differ
in the type of data removed and the re-arangement of remaining data. The
differences are explained below.</para>
	</listitem>
      </varlistentry>


      <varlistentry>
	<term>
	  <guiicon><inlinegraphic fileref="figures/label-four.png"></inlinegraphic>
	    Other operations on worksheets.
	  </guiicon>
	</term>
	<listitem>
	  <para>These menu entries do not group together logically. Each entry is
explained in detail below. </para>
	</listitem>
      </varlistentry>

</variablelist>



	<!--the list-->
       <para>
        This menu contains:
         <itemizedlist>
          <listitem>
           <para>
            <guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem>
            &mdash; Undoes the last action undertaken.
           </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
         <para>
          <guimenuitem>Redo</guimenuitem>
          &mdash; Reverses the previous undo operation, restoring 
          the worksheet to its orginal state.
         </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
         <para>
          <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem>
          &mdash; Remove the content in the currently selected cells and save it.
         </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
         <para>
          <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem>
          &mdash; Make a copy of the current selection to be pasted later.
         </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
         <para>
          <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem>
          &mdash; Paste whatever is in the cut buffer at the cursor.
         </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
         <para>
          <guimenuitem>Paste Special</guimenuitem>
          &mdash; Paste from the cut buffer, but with more options as to what to paste. 
          Useful for pasting just format, or just values, etc.
         </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
         <para>
          <guisubmenu>Clear -&gt;</guisubmenu>
          &mdash; This sub menu contains:
		    <itemizedlist>
			      <listitem>
			      <para>
			      <guimenuitem>All</guimenuitem>
			      &mdash;Clear every cell.
			      </para>
   		           </listitem>
			      <listitem>
			      <para>
			      <guimenuitem>Formats</guimenuitem>
			      &mdash;Clear the format from selected cells.
			      </para>
   		           </listitem>	
			      <listitem>
			      <para>
			      <guimenuitem>Comments</guimenuitem>
			      &mdash;FIXME
			      </para>
   		           </listitem>	
			      <listitem>
			      <para>
				  <guimenuitem>Content</guimenuitem>
			      &mdash;FIXME
			      </para>
   		           </listitem>	
   		       </itemizedlist>
    		   </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
         <para>
          <guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem>
          &mdash; Deletes the currently selected region
         </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
         <para>
          <guimenuitem>Delete Sheet</guimenuitem>
          &mdash; Select every cell in the worksheet.
         </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
         <para>
          <guimenuitem>Select All</guimenuitem>
          &mdash; Select every cell in the worksheet.
         </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
         <para>
          <guimenuitem>Goto Cell...</guimenuitem>
          &mdash; FIXME
         </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
         <para>
          <guimenuitem>Recalculate</guimenuitem>
          &mdash; FIXME
         </para>
        </listitem>
       </itemizedlist>
      </para>
	<!--end of list -->    

</sect1>


